# Blog app (`@pakfactory/blog`)

When editing files under **`apps/blog/`**, follow [`apps/blog/CLAUDE.md`](../../CLAUDE.md) and repo root [`AGENTS.md`](../../../../AGENTS.md).

**Quick rules:**

- **Routes:** `/` and `/[slug]` today; prefer Server Components; `revalidate = 60` by default.
- **Sanity:** queries only from `@pakfactory/sanity/queries`; `getSanityClient()` + `isSanityConfigured()`; no inline GROQ in pages.
- **AEO/GEO:** post pages should implement `generateMetadata` (OG + Twitter), `Article` JSON-LD, optional `FAQPage` JSON-LD for FAQ sections; entity-clear author.
- **Naming:** kebab-case `.tsx`; colocate in `_components/` under the route.
- **Tailwind:** no new tokens in `globals.css`; use `@pakfactory/ui` patterns.

**Skills:** `seo-content-writer`, `on-page-seo-auditor`, `geo-content-optimizer` (see root `CLAUDE.md`).
